  "description": "A stunning nighttime view of a city skyline illuminated by a vibrant fireworks display. The fireworks explode in brilliant bursts of white and gold against the dark sky, creating a dramatic contrast. Below, a long bridge stretches across a dark body of water, its lights reflecting on the surface. The city itself is a tapestry of lights, with buildings of varying heights and architectural styles forming a dense urban landscape. The scene is a dynamic blend of natural and man-made elements, capturing a moment of celebration and urban grandeur.",
